02:03.079 --> 02:05.917
But, uh... my God is music.

02:05.918 --> 02:07.917
Yeah?

02:07.918 --> 02:10.917
God appears in many ways.

02:10.918 --> 02:13.118
Yes. Yeah, it does.

02:13.918 --> 02:16.917
And...

02:16.918 --> 02:22.118
Have you ever felt
this dreadful passion?

02:24.420 --> 02:25.917
I...

02:25.918 --> 02:28.917
Close my eyes and I see her.

02:28.918 --> 02:30.917
I see her eyes.

02:30.918 --> 02:33.917
Her lips.

02:33.918 --> 02:35.917
I...

02:35.918 --> 02:37.917
She's coming.

02:37.918 --> 02:39.917
She's coming to town and

02:39.918 --> 02:43.917
I want to rid myself of this feeling,

02:43.918 --> 02:47.917
of this overwhelming feeling.

02:47.918 --> 02:51.917
Well, my relationship is with Jesus.

02:51.918 --> 02:54.917
So girlfriend advice isn't
really my specialty.

02:54.918 --> 02:56.917
But I can say that

02:56.918 --> 02:58.917
