18:29.918 --> 18:31.917
Very sophisticated.

18:31.918 --> 18:34.917
Very thoughtful.

18:34.918 --> 18:37.118
You got me thinking.

18:38.918 --> 18:40.917
And your technique with a bow.

18:40.918 --> 18:42.917
Phew...

18:42.918 --> 18:45.917
Even better than I remembered.

18:45.918 --> 18:47.917
It's very nice for one's technique

18:47.918 --> 18:50.917
