awareness about climate change.

19:01.918 --> 19:03.917
You got arrested, right?

19:03.918 --> 19:05.118
Yeah.

19:05.420 --> 19:06.917
Three times.

19:06.918 --> 19:08.917
Three times in Greenland.

19:08.918 --> 19:12.917
We succeeded.

19:12.918 --> 19:16.917
Anna Maria...

19:16.918 --> 19:17.917
Nothing changes.

19:17.918 --> 19:21.118
I guess your hair changed.

19:21.918 --> 19:23.917
That's very funny.

19:23.918 --> 19:26.118
But it's just hair.

19:27.918 --> 19:31.118
