- What?

19:52.918 --> 19:54.917
- No!
- No, no, no.

19:54.918 --> 19:55.917
No, no, no, no, no, no, no.

19:55.918 --> 19:56.917
No, she plays the oboe. No.

19:56.918 --> 19:58.917
She's my assistant.

19:58.918 --> 20:01.917
Then maybe I am seeing into the future.

20:01.918 --> 20:04.917
Anna Maria, look into my eyes.

20:04.918 --> 20:05.917
Calm down, look into my eyes.

20:05.918 --> 20:07.917
Okay, no, no, no. Breath in.
Breathe in a little bit.

20:07.918 --> 20:10.118
[screaming in Spanish]

20:15.918 --> 20:17.917
Oh, my God.

20:17.918 --> 20:20.917
The day you left to conduct for Oslo

20:20.918 --> 20:22.917
