21:40.918 --> 21:43.244
How do you feel then, mi Amor?

21:43.918 --> 21:45.917
I see what you're saying. Ow.

21:45.918 --> 21:49.118
You fucking disgust me.

21:49.294 --> 21:50.917
- I disgust you?
- Yeah.

